      "content": "it just feels like i was just existing alongside them, you know? like my whole life was built around this person. now the house is so quiet and i just feel so empty. it's like there's nothing left of me. if the pain is just going to keep being this heavy forever, why even bother trying to fight it? it just feels so exhausting to keep breathing when everything is just... void.",
